        <p style="color:#000;font-size:1.1em;">
    April 9, 2020<br>
In light of recent guidance from local and state agencies related to the unique health risks posed by the COVID-19 pandemic, the Compton Unified School District Board of Trustees at the April 8, 2020 Board of Trustees Meeting made a decision to extend school site <b>closure for the remainder of the school year</b>, unless further and different guidance is received from State and local officials. <br><br><a href="https://www.compton.k12.ca.us/news-release/news/2020/april/district-school-extended-closure">&gt; Click here to view full statement</a>
</p>
    


                            
    

    
